Releases
========

[Tails 4.18 was released on April 20](https://tails.boum.org/news/version_4.18).

Tails 4.19 is [scheduled for June 1](https://tails.boum.org/contribute/calendar).

## Changes and updates

* Removed "Synchronizing the system's clock" notification when connecting to Tor network

* Removed Poedit

